subject: Swimming
lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps opened the Olympic year with two victories at the Southern California Grand Prix in Long Beach, swimming his best times in the 100- and 500-yard freestyles Saturday night. Phelps won the 100 in 41.93 seconds, lowering the meet record he set last year.
